Starting Apache Kafka:

nohup ~/kafka/bin/kafka-server-start.sh ~/kafka/config/server.properties > ~/kafka/kafka.log 2>&1 &


Consumer :
~/kafka/bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181 --topic AbdulMOeed --from-beginning

Test Producer :

echo "Hello, World" | ~/kafka/bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --broker-list localhost:9092 --topic Tutorial > /dev/null



Kafka Resides in Kafka user :
home / kafka /kafka


Compiling Code :
sudo gcc FileName.c -lpcap -lrdkafka -lz -lpthread -lrt

Executing Code:
sudo ./a.out

